lyrics: The soft melodies of light music gently caressed the air, weaving a tapestry of tranquility around me. Each note seemed to possess a tender touch, as if whispering secrets of serenity to my weary soul. As I closed my eyes, I could feel the weight of the world slowly melting away, replaced by a sense of calmness and peace. The light music acted as a soothing balm, healing the wounds of a long, arduous day. It transported me to a realm where worries ceased to exist, and only the blissful harmony remained.
style: music on Japanese instruments, ninja running in the forest, soundtrack
